org.miniauth.oauth.credential.mapper

Class OAuthCredentialMapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.miniauth.oauth.credential.mapper.OAuthCredentialMapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CredentialMapper, OAuthTokenCredentialMapper
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    OAuthLocalCredentialMapper, OAuthLocalTokenCredentialMapper

    public abstract class OAuthCredentialMapper
extends Object
implements CredentialMapper, OAuthTokenCredentialMapper
    Service that returns a "secret" given a credential key. Specific implementation (based on the app requirement) should be inherited from this class.
